### Calculate Price | Iphone | GR country | Percentage coupon | Success
POST http://127.0.0.1:8337/calculate-price
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": 1,
  "taxNumber": "GR123456789",
  "couponCode": "NEW6"
}

### Calculate Price | Iphone | GR country | Fixed value coupon | Success
