### Execute Purchase | Iphone | IT country | Percentage coupon | Paypal | Success
POST http://127.0.0.1:8337/purchase
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": 1,
  "taxNumber": "IT12345678900",
  "couponCode": "NEW6",
  "paymentProcessor": "paypal"
}

